quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  91,1,"By the sun and its heat and brightness,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  91,2,"and by the moon as it follows it;"
  91,3,"and by the day as it displays the sun's glory,"
  91,4,"and by the night as it envelopes the sun;"{1},footnotes:1:1
  91,5,"and by the sky and by Him Who made it;"{1},footnotes:1:1
  91,6,"and by the earth and by Him Who stretched it out;"
  91,7,"and by the soul and by Him Who perfectly proportioned it,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  91,8,"and imbued it with (the consciousness of) its evil and its piety:"{1},footnotes:1:1
  91,9,"He who purifies it will prosper,"
  91,10,"and he who suppresses it will be ruined."{1},footnotes:1:1
  92,1,"By the night when it enshrouds,"
  92,2,"and by the day when it breaks in its glory,"
  92,3,"and by Him Who created the male and the female:"
  92,4,"surely your strivings are divergent."{1},footnotes:1:1
  92,5,"As for him who gave out his wealth (for Allah's sake) and abstained (from disobeying Him),"
  92,6,"and affirmed the Truth of goodness:"{1},footnotes:1:1
  92,7,"We shall facilitate for him the Way to Bliss."{1},footnotes:1:1
  92,8,"As for him who was a miser and behaved with aversion (to Allah),"
  92,9,"and denied the Truth of goodness:"{1},footnotes:1:1
  92,10,"We shall facilitate for him the way to Hardship,"{1},footnotes:1:1